metadata.name: Seductive eyes
metadata.description:
She is made of hot fire that is wild and full of passion. Her eyes may seduce you, but the heat of her soul will burn you, like the part of heaven that burns in hell.
Her gaze will consume you, she'll throw a ring of fire around your neck and capture you forever.
It will burn you and yet the depth of her look will make you be born again.

This work is hand-painted and has been scanned in high resolution.

6352 x 9546
